Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 02:38:34 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add 301 redirects for 14 legacy pre-migration URLs found via
 GA4 404 check

GA4 showed steady low-volume traffic (last 30 days) hitting 14 old
URLs from before the site's last restructuring -- old care-page paths
(pre-post-*), old service slugs (faq-cryolipolysis, slimming,
em-factloss-hifem, permanent-tattoo-removal) and a couple of
truncated/renamed slugs. None are linked from current site HTML, so
the traffic is external (old Google index entries, bookmarks, or
stale backlinks). Mapped each to its closest current equivalent page.

Also confirmed two other GA4-flagged 404s (/services-opal-radiant,
/laser-hair-removal-mumbai-1) are stale history -- both already
redirect correctly live, so no action needed there.
---
 _redirects | 32 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 32 insertions(+)

diff --git a/_redirects b/_redirects
index 49df05f..c7f683f 100644
--- a/_redirects
+++ b/_redirects
@@ -34,3 +34,35 @@
 /opal-blog/best-skin-laser-treatment-in-mumbai-complete-guide-to-laser-amp-aesthetic-clinic-services /services/ 301
 /opal-blog/q-switch-laser-for-indian-skin-safe-effective-or-overhyped/ /concerns/pigmentation-melasma 301
 /opal-blog/q-switch-laser-for-indian-skin-safe-effective-or-overhyped /concerns/pigmentation-melasma 301
